### 1. 헬스체크 (서버 실행 확인)
GET http://localhost:8081/health

###

### 2. 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "nickname": "tass"
}

###

### 3. 로그인 (accessToken + refreshToken 발급)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 4. 내 정보 조회 - 로그인 응답의 accessToken 복사해서 Bearer 뒤에 붙여넣기
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0YXNzQHpvbmkuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjozLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU2MjA4OTQsImV4cCI6MTc3NTYyMjY5NH0.vk7v8ogJm_kC4Dwan56rQi_LFqaKhO32O0yJ9zamcK9xSeNq00wHCfjguVffiqDR


###

### 5. Access Token 재발급 - 로그인 응답의 refreshToken 복사해서 붙여넣기
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0YXNzQHpvbmkuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjozLCJpYXQiOjE3NzUyNzE5NDQsImV4cCI6MTc3NTg3Njc0NH0.ngtKoVNaXe3OaacnZVgkoDDjPDrbEO1dJTlwoyewoZt9SFc2oH7IhikAZOzhBnOu"
}

###

